{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"48892b7aa1","title":"在中央工作会议上陈伯达同志发言时的插话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8d2a098aee","index":0,"year":1964,"month":12,"day":27,"articleId":"48892b7aa1","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"李雪峰","id":"d699b1a5e7","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7261b9b3f9","type":"title","text":"在中央工作会议上陈伯达同志发言时的插话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"48892b7aa1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e45c6f82f1","type":"paragraph","text":"（注：方括号内为陈伯达同志发言的有关内容）","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"48892b7aa1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ee99806982","type":"paragraph","text":"〔主要矛盾是什么？主席根据大家的意见作了总结。主要矛盾是社会主义和资本主义的矛盾。四清与四不清不能说明问题时性质。封建社会就是清官与贪官的问题。《四进士》就是反贪官的嘛！〕","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"48892b7aa1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"76b6f9632e","type":"paragraph","text":"巡抚出朝，地动山摇，可了不起哩！","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"48892b7aa1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9b88615169","type":"paragraph","text":"〔封建时代的清官实质上是假的。“三年清知府，十万雪花银。”清，在不同社会有不同的阶级内容。资本主义社会也有所谓清官，那些清官都是大财阀。〕","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"48892b7aa1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"31f3003019","type":"paragraph","text":"清朝刘锷的《老残游记》中说，清官害人，比贪官害人还厉害。后来一查，南北朝史中的《魏史》就有此说。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"48892b7aa1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ef2cac52f0","type":"paragraph","text":"〔内部矛盾那个时代没有？党内党外矛盾交叉，党内有党。国民党也有此问题。〕","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"48892b7aa1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3ab9ae9177","type":"paragraph","text":"我们党内至少有两派，一个是社会主义派，一个是资本主义派。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"48892b7aa1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c199fff5f7","type":"paragraph","text":"〔主席强调，要听各方面的话。好话，坏话，特别是反对的话，要耐心听。这是工作做的好坏的准则。〕","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"48892b7aa1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5c0e5cccc5","type":"paragraph","text":"讲话长了怎么办？李雪峰同志说的话，讲长了打零分。讲长了，让他讲长嘛！横直没人听嘛！","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"48892b7aa1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8decb5dbf7","type":"paragraph","text":"〔许多人忘记自己是从那里来的。不能忘本嘛！我这个人不参加革命，顶多是个小学教员、中学教员而已。〕","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"48892b7aa1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"940fa2638c","type":"paragraph","text":"大官是从小官来的，小官是从老百姓来的。我们都是从老百姓中来的，还是老百姓嘛！“蒋委员长”不姓蒋，姓郑，叫郑三发子，河南人氏，只知有母，不知有父，还不是老百姓变的？","index":11,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"48892b7aa1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4094dbbd4c","type":"paragraph","text":"〔主席常说，不要自以为是。乡干部当权，就以为自己的意见对。〕","index":12,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"48892b7aa1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"63ad62b495","type":"paragraph","text":"不要当了权，就是自己的意见对。自以为是，没有自以为不是的。为什么要开会？就是意贝不一致。一致了开会干什么？","index":13,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"48892b7aa1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e6202595c5","type":"paragraph","text":"〔不怕官，只怕管嘛！〕","index":14,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"48892b7aa1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"699da0b701","type":"paragraph","text":"小官怕大官，大官怕洋人。","index":15,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"48892b7aa1","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":386,"end":385}}}},"__N_SSG":true}